-9. Scan the About-page QR codes from a phone.
-10. Restart the Pi and confirm the server and kiosk return automatically.
+8. Open Admin and confirm Read Aloud Voice Status shows natural English and ready cloud/fallback voices.
+9. In Admin, configure Daily Exports, save Gmail settings, and send a test email.
+10. Scan the About-page QR codes from a phone.
+11. Restart the Pi and confirm the server and kiosk return automatically.
 
